WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.930 --> 00:00:06.390
- I have a really good friend
who is applying for a job,

2
00:00:06.390 --> 00:00:07.920
and he asked me for help getting ready

3
00:00:07.920 --> 00:00:09.487
for the job interview, and I told him,

4
00:00:09.487 --> 00:00:11.910
"Have you tried using
DeepResearch on Gemini?"

5
00:00:11.910 --> 00:00:13.170
And he said, no.

6
00:00:13.170 --> 00:00:16.020
So I told him, "Hey, why don't you ask,

7
00:00:16.020 --> 00:00:18.870
you know, Gemini Deep
Research to help you get ready

8
00:00:18.870 --> 00:00:21.720
by giving you a briefer on what you need

9
00:00:21.720 --> 00:00:23.550
to know in order to ace this interview.

10
00:00:23.550 --> 00:00:25.740
He got a ton of information
about the company,

11
00:00:25.740 --> 00:00:27.060
about the specific role,

12
00:00:27.060 --> 00:00:28.620
what kinds of questions he might be asked,

13
00:00:28.620 --> 00:00:30.240
and draft answers to those questions,

14
00:00:30.240 --> 00:00:32.040
and he ended up acing the interview.